{"tid":1641064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"下次再有阿蛇罪證，唔好再咁早放晒出黎","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:21:00.000Z","uid":302215,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f6e9de7132623aeda7e9a37b965e346e6168d9","tid":1641064,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"鑒於琴日上水站單野：<br />\n<br />\n蒙面男落閘上水站內持強光電筒照街坊 警方確認為便衣警<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640906</a><br />\n<br />\n然後？然後今天的驚謊記者會再次取消了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿蛇每次都帶大家遊花園，死都比佢地夾硬兜得翻生；就係因為事先已經睇晒片可以作故仔。雖然佢地已經冇乜誠信，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要個記者會徹底收皮；除左好似綠卡單野外，一定要搵到樣野係佢地講大話講到收唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等記者們可以每次都慢慢撚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果之前已經做過幾次好好的示範(如冇記錯)；例如Green Object單野；網上先留傳條低清片，後來過左一日的記者會後先再留出高清版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今次可以係好好的核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。試諗下拍片手足如果係流出條片之前，cut走部分關鍵內容，班餓底以為自己冇黃到的話今日個記者會一定會全力否認件事；撚完一日之後，再將完整高清版交比傳媒，阿蛇仲可以點解釋？唔通話資料有誤，原來果日有派餓底出動?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以提提大家，下次影到d好野千其唔好擠牙膏咁慢慢放出黎呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，反抗！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d8a9d2ad375ce63e58c14e915be975231b759ad8","tid":1641064,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:36:53.000Z","msg":"P牌放棄推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隨緣啦"},{"pid":"8b4c65bad1bb46bd8e197b45679c176cd007475a","tid":1641064,"uid":59863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"你就算當場踢爆佢殺人 <br />\n佢都可以話手頭上無資料 如屬實 會嚴肅處理"},{"pid":"eee6b40794efdbf94f958c18c7f5ca03a211b4e9","tid":1641064,"uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:38:26.000Z","msg":"facebook 控制唔到架"},{"pid":"fd1f0b709a33a5ab66dc2df34eb8619d8c4ef048","tid":1641064,"uid":307358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"Agger 幫手推啊各位"},{"pid":"4cf933246f830f8d63d0d8812032b5576089b3a2","tid":1641064,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3PNSB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3PNSB7.png&h=70fa4b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4UBLW8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4UBLW8.png&h=10505b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"289842a63806d2fd38364fe0b08d2fb4afb701a2","tid":1641064,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b4c65bad1bb46bd8e197b45679c176cd007475a","tid":1641064,"uid":59863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"你就算當場踢爆佢殺人 <br />\n佢都可以話手頭上無資料 如屬實 會嚴肅處理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"所以個重點係，先引佢地認左；之後再踢爆"},{"pid":"4c68149f5f20fffd32c3126961d6eff37aeb98b7","tid":1641064,"uid":283344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"資料出錯唔得嘅"}]}